:Capacity_for_Effective_Climate-related_Management rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                   rdfs:subClassOf :Capacity ;
                                                   rdfs:label "capacity for effective climate-related management"@en ;
                                                   <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Provisional> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Capacity_for_Effective_Climate-related_Planning
:Capacity_for_Effective_Climate-related_Planning rdf:type owl:Class ;
