###  https://www.w3id.org/sco#SCO_0000041
<https://www.w3id.org/sco#SCO_0000041> rdfs:comment """ClimOO Ontology comment:
We classified resilience and vulnerability as properties of complex systems as widely recognized as such (see for instance Gunderson & Holling (2002), Holling (1973), and Van Meerbeek et al. (2021)). Implementation will deal with other ClimOO-SDC2 realizable entity/quality classes as needed.

Gunderson, L. H., & Holling, C. S. (2002). Panarchy: Understanding Transformations in Human and Natural Systems. Island Press.
Holling, C. S. (1973). Resilience and Stability of Ecological Systems. Annu. Rev. Ecol. Syst., 4, 1–23.
Van Meerbeek, K., Jucker, T., & Svenning, J.-C. (2021). Unifying the concepts of stability and resilience in ecology. J. Ecol., 109(9), 3114–3132."""@en .


